Class BrokerChannel

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.saasovation.common.port.adapter.messaging.rabbitmq.BrokerChannel
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Exchange, Queue

    public abstract class BrokerChannel
extends java.lang.Object
    I am an abstract base class for all channels to the RabbitMQ message broker.
